description:
Today’s show is all about exploring your deepest desires! Emily is joined by the stars of Showtime’s steamy new late night show Submission to discuss love, kink and the erotic nature of consent.

 

Skin Diamond and Ashlynn Yennie share some of their most intimate stories, both onscreen and off, and reveal what really goes on in a Dom/Sub relationship. The stars open up about their own love lives, divulge details about their sultry shared sex scene and even answer Emily’s Top 5 Sex Questions.

 

From puppy play to post-breakup vengeance to the truth behind the BDSM subculture, this podcast is chock full of fantasies you won’t want to miss out on!
